<h1>Welcome to Candidate Match!</h1><br>

<h2>What is Candidate Match?</h2>
<br>
<p>Candidate Match is a system designed to help you find out who to vote for in an election. All you have to do is fill out a short questionnaire and a breakdown of how your choices compare with all of the candidates will be shown. </p>
<br>
<p>Please click on voters and select an election to get started.</p>
<br>
<p>If you are a candidate, please click on 'Candidate Login' and enter your Username and password to proceed.</p>
